Class CexPathStates

  • java.lang.Object
    • cex.CexPathStates
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PathFullInfo

    public class CexPathStates
extends java.lang.Object
implements PathFullInfo
    Class to store a counterexample/witness comprising a single path, represented as a list of states, stored as State objects.
